 4\alpha(1 - \alpha) = k^2x_0^2 \rightarrow 4\frac{kx_0^2}{4y_0}\left(1 - \frac{kx_0^2}{4y_0}\right) = k^2x_0^2 \\ \frac{k}{y_0}\cdot\frac{4y_0 - kx_0^2}{4y_0} = k^2 \\ 4y_0 -kx_0^2 = 4ky_0^2 \\ kx_0^2 = 4y_0 - 4ky_0^2 = 4y_0(1 - 4ky_0) 
